        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3817642789" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4984490364443479848">Extremely profound book on how we humans have lived in the past, how we got here to our current predicament, and what changes we need to make to live in harmony with our environment and planet. the first section is rough, but stay with it, and by the third section you&apos;re ready to hear his hopeful message of changes we can all make to live in peace with our world.</span>
  <span id="freeText4984490364443479848" style="display:none">Extremely profound book on how we humans have lived in the past, how we got here to our current predicament, and what changes we need to make to live in harmony with our environment and planet. the first section is rough, but stay with it, and by the third section you're ready to hear his hopeful message of changes we can all make to live in peace with our world.</span>
